Some Copyright information: it's now forbidden to redistribute tracker
as a stand-alone program. I'm fed up of getting incomplete bug-reports.
Be sure to at least include the contents of the Doc directory with your
version, and full directions to get back the source.
THANKS.
For ANY bug-report, DON'T FORGET TO INCLUDE *FULL* VERSION INFORMATION,
including
- tracker source version
- the architecture on which you've compiled it.
- any change from the standard distribution as available from aminet.

